question: Display middle data analysts and software developers.
sql_query1:
SELECT Software_Developers.name
FROM Software_Developers
WHERE Software_Developers.grade = "Middle"
UNION
SELECT Data_Analysts.name
FROM Data_Analysts
WHERE Data_Analysts.grade = "Middle"
sql_query2:
SELECT Software_Developers.name
FROM Software_Developers
UNION
SELECT Data_Analysts.name
FROM Data_Analysts
WHERE Data_Analysts.grade = "Middle"
interpretation1: Which software developers and data analysts have a middle grade?
interpretation2: List all software developers and also show middle data analysts.
